            "title": "舜宇上月手機鏡頭與手機攝像模組出貨量按年均錄雙位數跌幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學(02382)公布，今年3月份手機鏡頭與手機攝像模組出貨量，按年均錄雙位數跌幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，出現上述情況，主要因為公司專注於中高端案子，且產品結構較去年同期改善所致。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在3月份，舜宇光學的手機鏡頭出貨百9431.6萬件，按年跌16.3%，按月也減少2.9%；手機攝像模組出貨量3731.4萬件，按年跌10.9%，按月則提升5.5%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/02382-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/02382-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內車載鏡頭出貨量982.1萬件，按年升16.5%，按月也增11.5%，主要受惠客戶端需求提升；玻璃球面鏡片出貨量216.2萬件，按年升10.8%，按月大增65.5%；其他鏡頭出貨量695萬件，按年顯著增加61.1%，按月微升4.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於手機攝像模組以外的其他光電產品上月出貨量，則為288.8萬件，按年降11.7%，按月升10.8%。顯微儀器出貨量2676.8萬件，按年及按月分別大升78.8%及46.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844558-%e8%88%9c%e5%ae%87%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e9%8f%a1%e9%a0%ad%e8%88%87%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e6%94%9d%e5%83%8f%e6%a8%a1%e7%b5%84%e5%87%ba%e8%b2%a8%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%9d%87%e9%8c%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 16:45:38",
