        {
            "title": "安德利果汁料首季純利按年升50%至70%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安德利果汁(02218)發盈喜，預期今年首季歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤8007萬元(人民幣．下同)至9087萬元，按年升50%至70%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_fi_安德利果汁_source-web_官網_fb.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_fi_安德利果汁_source-web_官網_fb.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">預計期內歸屬上市公司股東並扣除非經常性損益的淨利潤約7903萬至8983萬元，按年也增長32%至50%。該公司解釋，首季盈利提升，主要因為客戶訂單需求增加，濃綜果汁的銷售量按年大幅增長所致。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844517-%e5%ae%89%e5%be%b7%e5%88%a9%e6%9e%9c%e6%b1%81%e6%96%99%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%8750%e8%87%b370",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_02218_source-web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 16:30:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲股市上升　德股升逾8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲主要股市早段顯著上揚。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦富時指數較早時報8148點，升469點，升幅6.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">巴黎CAC指數報7161點，升298點，升幅4.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法蘭克福DAX指數報 21249點，升1579點，升幅8.03%。</p>\n</div>",
